      "rationale": "Ti-6Al-4V material properties from lot-specific tensile test certificates (n=3 coupons). Screw and rod geometry digitized via CMM (±0.005 mm). UHMWPE block modulus from supplier datasheet with ±10% uncertainty bound. One-at-a-time sensitivity analysis confirmed stiffness QoI most sensitive to rod diameter (±3.2%) and least sensitive to block modulus (±0.8%)."
