      "rationale": "N=11 constructs assembled from production-representative 7.5 mm non-cannulated pedicle screws and 5.5 mm titanium rods. Hardware sourced from two manufacturing lots with full traceability. Construct assembly performed by trained technician per device IFU. Sample size exceeds ASTM F1717 minimum."
