      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Test conditions span at least two load levels or two environmental conditions to support interpolation; environmental controls documented.",
      "rationale": "Testing performed at a single quasi-static loading rate (2 mm/min) per ASTM F1717. Ambient temperature and humidity monitored and within specification, but only one load condition tested. This factor achieves Gradation 2 rather than the required Gradation 3; risk accepted given that F1717 is a standardized single-condition protocol and the decision consequence is Medium."
    },
    {
