      "rationale": "Construct stiffness and yield force are the primary regulatory QoIs for 510(k) submissions involving spinal pedicle screw systems. Force at 40 mm displacement characterizes post-yield behavior relevant to fatigue life estimation. All three QoIs are specified in ASTM F1717 and directly address the COU decision question."
